                    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-4">? Best Practices</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2" style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
                        <li><strong>Use Labels:</strong> Provide AriaLabel for descriptive group purpose</li>
                        <li><strong>Related Buttons:</strong> Group only logically related buttons together</li>
                        <li><strong>Consistent Variants:</strong> Maintain button variant consistency within groups</li>
                        <li><strong>Icon Clarity:</strong> Always combine icons with tooltips or text labels</li>
                        <li><strong>Size Consistency:</strong> Keep button sizes uniform within a group</li>
                        <li><strong>Mobile First:</strong> Use ResponsiveVertical for better mobile experience</li>
